# Code style

- Vanilla HTML, CSS, JS only. No frameworks, no build tools.
- No inline styles unless absolutely unavoidable.
- No hardcoded values anywhere — use tokens.
- Class names in kebab-case (hero-title, not heroTitle).
- One component at a time. Confirm it works before moving on.
- File structure:
  - index.html → HTML structure
  - css/tokens.css → design tokens only, no styles
  - css/base.css → resets and global styles
  - css/components.css → all component styles
  - js/main.js → minimal JS only